=> END

~ mcbucket_med_given_after_zanopram
Hmmm. The Old Man seems unaffected. His sleep is deep.
=> END

~ toilet_flush_weak

You flush the toilet. It seems to have a weak flow.
=> END

~ medicine_cabinet_interrupt

AIda: Hey patient #122, that cabinet is reserved for clinical staff. 
AIda: If you are experiencing discomfort, I can assist with approved medication.
Player: (Huh. Looks like I can’t open the medicine cabinet while she’s still around.)
Player: (Is there anyway I can send her to the other room?)
=> END

~ mcbucket_not_put_to_sleep
Player: (The Old Man still seems to be up.)
Player: (I better take care of him before returning to Sergey.)
=> END

